item.title: CVE-2018-2738|2024-10-03T20:23:46.173Z -- oracle%20corporation -- retail%20central%20office
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle Retail Central Office component of Oracle Retail Applications (subcomponent: Security). Supported versions that are affected are 13.4.9, 14.0.4 and 14.1.3. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle Retail Central Office. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized update, insert or delete access to some of Oracle Retail Central Office accessible data as well as unauthorized read access to a subset of Oracle Retail Central Office accessible data. CVSS 3.0 Base Score 6.5 (Confidentiality and Integrity impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.0/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N).
